element.name: Fancy that! Lugg a vault up the wrong mountain by ThePeatHags (adopted by toczygroszek), Unknown Cache (3/4)
element.description: A hike through the Wicklow mountains to find this cache but....

long-description.p: Before you set out you must first locate and obtain TB29HKW. Bring it with you. Without it you will not be able to locate and find the cache. We won't tell you much about the cache, except that it is under a big rock in the Wicklow mountains so dress and prepare appropriately (rain gear, good shoes, etc.). After that, it's up to you!

The cache is not at listed coordinates (top of Knocknacloghoge mountain). To locate the cache you have to use information attached to TravelBug TB29HKW.
Important: Logs without an actual note in the logbook will be deleted!
Please make sure you have locked the cache and its cover well. Thanks for cooperation. Good luck!

ul.li:
2009-10-11T19:00:00Z : Found it by daraconn
Having found the travel bug last weekend, today I went with Ausra and Shiro to climb Knocknacloghoge and find the cache. It's the only summit in the area I had never visited before. Having considered a number of possible approaches, we decided to approach from the west, which is fairly flat, wet and boggy terrain with no paths. Tough going at times, but it got easier as we approached the hill and started climbing. It was very misty when we set out, but by the time we reached the summit the mist was starting to clear a little and we had some views of the lakes. When we finally got back to the car all three of us were up to our knees in muck. It was a 9 km round-trip, but some of those kilometres were pretty hard work!

2009-08-23T19:10:45Z : Enable Listing by toczygroszek
After 3 years non-existence of this cache I'm enabling it now. Necessary TB will place soon in some cache.

2009-08-23T19:00:00Z : Found it by theswerve
Very windy on top yesterday...good hide...Good to see this one back in action...TFTC..

Cache replaced in new location

2009-08-23T19:00:00Z : Didn't find it by toczygroszek
Tried find old container but looks is gone. [V]
Don't worry, brand new container is placed in new location and cache will be acivated soon. [:D]
